chart_description: This chart displays the number of cache events per second in Netdata's main database engine cache, including aggressive evictions, critical evictions, and critical flushes.

dimension_descriptions.evictions aggressive: The number of times cache entries were evicted aggressively because the cache was full and new entries were added.
dimension_descriptions.evictions critical: The number of times cache entries were evicted critically because the cache was critically full and new entries were added.
dimension_descriptions.flushes critical: The number of times entries in the cache were flushed critically because the cache was critically full and new entries were added.
